data.description: Inviting 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home with spacious living areas, ideal for both entertaining and everyday living. Massive bonus room that offers the versatility to be used as additional bedroom or flex space. Updated interior showcases newer laminate plank flooring and open shelving in kitchen. Expansive backyard provides your perfect retreat. Each bedroom offers comfort and ample natural light. Master bedroom featured tray ceiling and a roomy bathroom with a large soaking tub and separate shower. Enjoy the convenience of a short commute to Fayetteville and Fort Liberty. This home seamlessly blends style with functionality, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere for its future owners! $2,000 closing credit being offered to buyer at closing!
